name: Man of Steel
description:
Three colour silk screen print - black, silver and red, in a limited edition of 12.

Paper size: 60 x 42 cm (approx. A2 Landscape) 

Printed on John Purcell South Bank Smooth Paper, 250gsm.

Print is signed and editioned.

Unframed.

Postage - Prints are rolled and posted in a tube by Royal Mail First Class Recorded Delivery. Postage can take 3-5 days.
